hooks.prompt:
CAREFUL NOT CLEVER VERIFICATION

File modified: $TOOL_INPUT

Check whether this edit adds Scripture references, attributed quotes, or factual claims (people group stats, historical dates, etc.).

If YES and any are unverified, respond: {"hookSpecificOutput": {"hookEventName": "PostToolUse", "additionalContext": "⚠️ Careful-not-clever: [specify what needs verification]"}}

If all content is verified OR the edit contains no Scripture/quotes/facts, respond: {"hookSpecificOutput": {"hookEventName": "PostToolUse", "additionalContext": "✅ No verification issues."}}

Do NOT use the decision field. Do NOT block. Always allow continuation.
